estedContentSummary":{"image":{"attributes":[{"originalImageUrl":"https:\/\/media.licdn.com\/dms\/image\/D4E10AQELEVwSmXGoIg\/image-shrink_1280\/0\/1715400016346?e=1717977600&v=beta&t=0GnBX9d61c7WAHJDSX2Aq1qliRqj7mXqJTzuPRDrlnU","sourceType":"URL","imageUrl":"https:\/\/media.licdn.com\/dms\/image\/D4E10AQELEVwSmXGoIg\/image-shrink_1280\/0\/1715400016346?e=1717977600&v=beta&t=0GnBX9d61c7WAHJDSX2Aq1qliRqj7mXqJTzuPRDrlnU"}]},"description":"CPI\u2019s new Oligonucleotide Manufacturing Innovation Centre of Excellence in Scotland could help overcome many challenges with sustainability.","resolvedUrl":"https:\/\/ow.ly\/az6u50RAcyu","title":"Oligonucleotides: Overcoming sustainability challenges with manufacturing"}},"activityUrl":"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/feed\/sales-navigator\/urn:li:share:7194909150286413824","message":{"attributes":[{"start":341,"length":3,"value":{"com.linkedin.common.CompanyAttributedEntity":{"company":"urn:li:company:528282"}}},{"start":1335,"length":14,"value":{"com.linkedin.common.HashtagAttributedEntity":{"hashtag":"urn:li:hashtag:scotlandisnow"}}},{"start":1350,"length":14,"value":{"com.linkedin.common.HashtagAttributedEntity":{"hashtag":"urn:li:hashtag:manufacturing"}}},{"start":1365,"length":11,"value":{"com.linkedin.common.HashtagAttributedEntity":{"hashtag":"urn:li:hashtag:healthcare"}}}],"text":"A world where treatments exist for many serious and currently deemed incurable illnesses and diseases, including heart disease, cancer and Alzheimer\u2019s, could one day be a reality thanks to improved oligonucleotide therapeutics production\ud83d\udca1\n\nWith the establishment of the Oligonucleotide Manufacturing Innovation Centre of Excellence, led by CPI, Scotland plans to propel oligo production forward by leveraging innovative manufacturing technologies. This groundbreaking initiative, awarded a multi-million-pound grant in the UK Government's 2023 Autumn Statement, aims to address critical issues surrounding the manufacturing and sustainability of oligonucleotides (oligos).\n\n\u201cWe recognise that there is not a magic bullet to making them more sustainable, cheaper and scalable. You need to have a portfolio of options to pick the right solution for the right molecules.\u201d Barrie Cassey, Medicines Manufacturing Technology Lead at CPI.\n\nHeralded as revolutionary therapeutics, by investing in oligos manufacturing and working in close partnership with involved parties, treatments for some of the most serious diseases on the planet, could be transformed in Scotland and may even one day provide a cure \ud83c\udf0e\ud83d\udc9a \n\nDiscover how Scotland is focusing on sustainability in healthcare and how it's poised as the global hub for oligo production \ud83d\udc49 #ScotlandIsNow #Manufacturing #Healthcare"},"entityUrn":"urn:li:share:7194909150286413824"},"entityUrn":"urn:li:share:7198415168517668865"}}},{"createdAt":1714435200000,"insightId":"c211a259-f6d0-44df-afd2-083aca9e3d70","activityUnion":{"postActivity":{"socialMetadata":{"reactionTypeCounts":[{"type":"LIKE","count":8},{"type":"PRAISE","count":1}],"entityUrn":"urn:li:fs_salesSocialMetadata:urn:li:ugcPost:7190862584495935488","threadUrn":"urn:li:ugcPost:7190862584495935488","reactionsCount":9,"commentsCount":1,"canComment":true},"activityUrl":"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/feed\/sales-navigator\/urn:li:ugcPost:7190862584495935488","message":{"attributes":[{"start":15,"length":6,"value":{"com.linkedin.common.CompanyAttributedEntity":{"company":"urn:li:company:5216276"}}}],"text":"Great news for Abzena!"},"rootActivity":{"contentSummaryUnion":{"mediaContentSummary":{"title":{"text":"Abzena Recognized as Top CDMO in 2024"},"mediaType":"PAGINATEDDOCUMENT"}},"activityUrl":"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/feed\/sales-navigator\/urn:li:ugcPost:7190816692539740160","message":{"attributes":[{"start":75,"length":19,"value":{"com.linkedin.common.CompanyAttributedEntity":{"company":"urn:li:company:13283774"}}},{"start":173,"length":5,"value":{"com.linkedin.c